# Tosaporn Pompan project

## Auto-read before acting

| Task | Read first |
|------|------------|
| UI, layout, colors, hero, luxury styling | [DESIGN.md](../../DESIGN.md) |
| Products, copy, social links, SEO text | [content/README.md](../../content/README.md) + `content/site.json` / `content/products.json` |
| Cursor rules or AGENTS.md changes | create-rule skill |
| PR / CI babysitting | babysit skill |

Do not guess brand colors, hero layout, or content file locations — read the doc above.

## Design non-negotiables (approved look — locked)

- Luxury Japanese artisan: charcoal + gold + ivory, Noto Serif headings
- Primary goal: Facebook + TikTok follows (no shop, no Instagram unless asked)
- **Hero:** `IMG_3598.JPG` full-viewport **background** + title/tagline/**luxury** buttons **overlaid** — never revert to side card or framed hero box
- Gallery/studio: gold frames; hero: no frame
- Content in `content/*.json` only

Full spec: [DESIGN.md](../../DESIGN.md)

## Dev commands

```bash
npm run dev       # clears .next, then dev
npm run build     # clears .next + out, then build
npm run preview   # serve out/ locally
```

If port 3000 is stuck, stop old `next dev` processes before starting again.

## Code style

Follow [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md): minimal diffs, match existing CSS module patterns, no Tailwind.
